  "$comment": "Agentic COBOL \u2014 natural-language acceptance tests for fleet agent routing. Canonical prompt set for the InvestorClaw + InvestorClaude fleet. Single source of truth for both the InvestorClaw cross-runtime pilot (OpenClaw / ZeroClaw / Hermes) and the InvestorClaude text harness (Claude Code). Promoted from SKILL.toml \u00a7 NATURAL LANGUAGE QUERY MAP plus the v2.3.4 starter set; expected_routes updated for v2.5.0 consolidated surface. v2.5.0. See harness/cobol/AGENTIC_COBOL_SPEC.md for methodology.",
